","text":"The values returned by successive calls to this method"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"appear in the order that the tasks "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"completed"}]},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"not in the order that those tasks were added to the task group."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["group.addTask { 1 }","group.addTask { 2 }","","print(await group.next())","\/\/ Prints either \"2\" or \"1\"."]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If there aren’t any pending tasks in the task group,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method returns "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which lets you write the following"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to wait for a single task to complete:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["if let first = try await group.next() {","   return first","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It also lets you write code like the following"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to wait for all the child tasks to complete,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"collecting the values they returned:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["while let first = try await group.next() {","   collected += value","}","return collected"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Awaiting on an empty group"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"immediately returns "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" without suspending."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also use a "},{"code":"for","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"code":"await","type":"codeVoice"